  <!-- EN: psilocap -->
  <Drug_Psilocap.label>靈感菇</Drug_Psilocap.label>
  <!-- EN: The fruiting body of a hallucinogenic fungus. When eaten it produces vivid sensory experiences and lifts mood. There is a small chance to immediately induce a catatonic state, or creatively inspire the user. Psilocaps are not addictive, but can cause overdoses if eaten in large quantities.\n\nSome cultures use psilocaps for religious ceremonies, while many others have outlawed the mushrooms entirely. -->
  <Drug_Psilocap.description>這是一種具有迷幻特性的真菌的子實體。食用後會誘發生動的感官體驗並提升心情。食用者有小概率立即進入緊張症狀態，或激發其進入狂熱。靈感菇不具成癮性，但大量食用可能會導致用藥過量。\n\n某些文化會在宗教儀式中使用靈感菇，而許多其他文化則完全禁止這種菇類。</Drug_Psilocap.description>
  
</LanguageData>